Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:43.39,en,,0,0,0,,We managed to put Chu Tu behind bars, but the operation was a costly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.43,en,,0,0,0,,You destroyed the squatter village,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.87,en,,0,0,0,,and the government had to relocate the families
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.67,en,,0,0,0,,and pay damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:54.11,en,,0,0,0,,During the operation, you damaged the shopping centre as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.83,en,,0,0,0,,We paid well over a million for the chandelier alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:12.59,en,,0,0,0,,The taxpayers know police work doesn't come cheaply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:16.91,en,,0,0,0,,But they don't expect to pay the cost of someone's heroics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.35,en,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you use the stairs? Did you have to destroy that chandelier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.59,en,,0,0,0,,Do you always have to be different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.66,en,,0,0,0,,You're right. The force doesn't need superstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.43,en,,0,0,0,,We need disciplined policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.99,en,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:09.43,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, the operation succeeded through team effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.51,en,,0,0,0,,not just because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.79,en,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful we didn't fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.15,en,,0,0,0,,The bosses wanted you disciplined
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.43,en,,0,0,0,,for holding me hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.19,en,,0,0,0,,I managed to talk them out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.42,en,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.23,en,,0,0,0,,I worry about your individualism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.39,en,,0,0,0,,You're just a police officer. Don't forget that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:52.11,en,,0,0,0,,As of today, you're back in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.31,en,,0,0,0,,You'll be assigned wherever needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.27,en,,0,0,0,,You mean he'll be an errand boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.99,en,,0,0,0,,I think you'll be very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.15,en,,0,0,0,,What else do you do besides giving out tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.79,en,,0,0,0,,Calling all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.55,en,,0,0,0,,There's been a serious road accident at the Industrial Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.86,en,,0,0,0,,Traffic is at a standstill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.63,en,,0,0,0,,All units in the area, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.59,en,,0,0,0,,May, go home. I'm working now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.63,en,,0,0,0,,Just think of me as a member of the public
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.55,en,,0,0,0,,who wants to talk to a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.95,en,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.34,en,,0,0,0,,I think you look very smart in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.63,en,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I'm on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.23,en,,0,0,0,,I've brought you a cold drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.70,en,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.43,en,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.35,en,,0,0,0,,-I can't drink here. -Go on, you need a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.90,en,,0,0,0,,If I have a drink, pretty soon I'll need the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.59,en,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.43,en,,0,0,0,,May, I'll get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:42.27,en,,0,0,0,,Hello, superhero! You still haven't been sacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.07,en,,0,0,0,,You're lucky you're not in jail with Chu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.47,en,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.39,en,,0,0,0,,Three Swiss doctors said I had only three months to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.51,en,,0,0,0,,It's called compassionate release.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.27,en,,0,0,0,,Three months can pass quickly. Very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.47,en,,0,0,0,,My boss will be alive long after you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.67,en,,0,0,0,,Don't you know you're threatening him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.32,en,,0,0,0,,Really? In that case, he can sue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.75,en,,0,0,0,,Just be careful! Drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.38,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.71,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, Chu Tu is out of jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:51.79,en,,0,0,0,,I know. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.31,en,,0,0,0,,You already knew? That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.47,en,,0,0,0,,If you'd never nabbed a thief, who would you have to be scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:10:00.87,en,,0,0,0,,Just remember, there are 250,000 Royal Hong Kong Police at your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.83,en,,0,0,0,,Bill, are there really 250,000 police in Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.95,en,,0,0,0,,We're always recruiting new blood. Didn't you see our newspaper ad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.99,en,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for? Go on patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.99,en,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've talked to Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.03,en,,0,0,0,,He said you could carry a gun, even after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.14,en,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.67,en,,0,0,0,,The show and dinner were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:31.11,en,,0,0,0,,-You don't seem very happy. -Really? I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.66,en,,0,0,0,,I wish you had enjoyed it as much as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:41.35,en,,0,0,0,,-Are you worried about Chu? -No. But I'm just being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:50.79,en,,0,0,0,,-Maybe next week... -Hey, superhero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.11,en,,0,0,0,,Off duty already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.66,en,,0,0,0,,-What are you doing here? -I can park here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.75,en,,0,0,0,,You can't give me a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.35,en,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you must have a nice view from Flat B of the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.83,en,,0,0,0,,-Am I right? -Go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.95,en,,0,0,0,,How did you find this address?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:18.63,en,,0,0,0,,It's amazing what information you can get with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:23.51,en,,0,0,0,,People will do anything for money, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.71,en,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.07,en,,0,0,0,,There's a narrow stairwell in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.83,en,,0,0,0,,If there ever happened to be a fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.75,en,,0,0,0,,it would spread quickly through the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:35.87,en,,0,0,0,,Because of the narrow access,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.95,en,,0,0,0,,the fire brigade couldn't get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:41.59,en,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend's cute. You'd better keep a close eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:46.95,en,,0,0,0,,If she were to get her pretty ass burnt, it'd ruin her marriage prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.75,en,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.27,en,,0,0,0,,Oh, hero, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.39,en,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.59,en,,0,0,0,,It's my fault really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.51,en,,0,0,0,,Policemen like me have lots of enemies. You face threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:17.11,en,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:21.67,en,,0,0,0,,If you had no enemies, that would mean you'd never caught a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.83,en,,0,0,0,,Think you could stay somewhere else for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.91,en,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. They're just morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.51,en,,0,0,0,,No. We'd just stand out while they stayed hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:34.51,en,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. 191 move to my aunt's and hide out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.51,en,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:39.59,en,,0,0,0,,But if you drop a vase on him, I'll definitely be the dead one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.58,en,,0,0,0,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:58.67,en,,0,0,0,,Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.91,en,,0,0,0,,You're on your own? Where's Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.23,en,,0,0,0,,He's still on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.99,en,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.79,en,,0,0,0,,I'm not against you dating a policeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:10.43,en,,0,0,0,,but I don't want him to spend too much time on his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.75,en,,0,0,0,,He's stubborn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.23,en,,0,0,0,,But a man should do his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:17.75,en,,0,0,0,,That's why he has lots of enemies and you have to move back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.75,en,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't worry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.99,en,,0,0,0,,That way, he doesn't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.78,en,,0,0,0,,He ought to worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.03,en,,0,0,0,,-Who are they? -They're the ones from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.15,en,,0,0,0,,I guess superhero isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.15,en,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.27,en,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:37.11,en,,0,0,0,,-What do you want? -We have a score to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.39,en,,0,0,0,,I just want to know where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.63,en,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.59,en,,0,0,0,,You must be her mother. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.07,en,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.66,en,,0,0,0,,You call me a bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.38,en,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I'm the bastard son of a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.23,en,,0,0,0,,-I'm not afraid of you. -Don't waste time with him. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:01.47,en,,0,0,0,,Auntie, why has your daughter fallen for a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.91,en,,0,0,0,,That could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:06.11,en,,0,0,0,,Living on the 19th floor is dangerous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.95,en,,0,0,0,,What if you took a fall while cleaning the windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.75,en,,0,0,0,,It would take more than glue to fix you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.15,en,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.75,en,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.99,en,,0,0,0,,-Go away! -Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.15,en,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.95,en,,0,0,0,,Don't grab my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.18,en,,0,0,0,,You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.99,en,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:33.19,en,,0,0,0,,Easy, she's just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.58,en,,0,0,0,,Count yourself lucky. If you were a man, you'd be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.31,en,,0,0,0,,-I won't forget this! -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.51,en,,0,0,0,,You just watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.71,en,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.99,en,,0,0,0,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.68,en,,0,0,0,,It's your job that brings the bad guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.71,en,,0,0,0,,Look. May was badly beaten because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.63,en,,0,0,0,,I've told you to stop seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.39,en,,0,0,0,,Did John Ko attack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.35,en,,0,0,0,,I started hitting him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.15,en,,0,0,0,,He just hit me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.75,en,,0,0,0,,And they knocked me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.23,en,,0,0,0,,My backside still hurts. Now I can't sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.03,en,,0,0,0,,How did they know you'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.91,en,,0,0,0,,They followed her, that's how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.51,en,,0,0,0,,They're watching us from across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.91,en,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.19,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.99,en,,0,0,0,,He should go and scold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.31,en,,0,0,0,,If it's as easy as all that, then I'll be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.87,en,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.63,en,,0,0,0,,What else do you do besides bullying women?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.67,en,,0,0,0,,It's my favourite hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.19,en,,0,0,0,,Get the bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.07,en,,0,0,0,,You know the law, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.39,en,,0,0,0,,They may have threatened her, but an arrest requires evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.95,en,,0,0,0,,Don't you know you're a policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.95,en,,0,0,0,,I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.19,en,,0,0,0,,That's not a good reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.63,en,,0,0,0,,He reacted like anyone else would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.83,en,,0,0,0,,He's not anyone else. He's a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.95,en,,0,0,0,,What you've done is disgraceful! It's a disgrace to the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:20.47,en,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. If a policeman fails to respond to a personal threat, that's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.47,en,,0,0,0,,-And it disgraces the law too. -You're a show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:28.35,en,,0,0,0,,You won't let us forget you arrested Chu. How can I explain this to the chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.51,en,,0,0,0,,You don't have to. I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.19,en,,0,0,0,,You think that will solve the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:46.82,en,,0,0,0,,Why not? This is probably the best solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.51,en,,0,0,0,,191 leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.51,en,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support in times past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:54.58,en,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.90,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.55,en,,0,0,0,,If that's your last word...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.67,en,,0,0,0,,then try to find a less stressful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.31,en,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.46,en,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.99,en,,0,0,0,,You think you can do anything you want just because you're cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.14,en,,0,0,0,,Don't you know the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:16.63,en,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me up just like that! Kill me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.11,en,,0,0,0,,Shut up and sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.76,en,,0,0,0,,I'm not signing anything. No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:24.11,en,,0,0,0,,I'll sue you for every penny you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.39,en,,0,0,0,,I've got lots of money. I'll get a lawyer. I'll sue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.86,en,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.43,en,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:38.51,en,,0,0,0,,See? You saw this officer try to assault me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:43.83,en,,0,0,0,,He wants to beat me up like before, when he hit me and broke my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:47.46,en,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that. Would you dare to beat me up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.31,en,,0,0,0,,Come on. What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:53.91,en,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm going to sue you. You're going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.67,en,,0,0,0,,These youngsters have no patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.35,en,,0,0,0,,Bill, why didn't you ask him to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.42,en,,0,0,0,,You should have said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.12,en,,0,0,0,,I thought you meant throw him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.43,en,,0,0,0,,Now that I know what that gesture means, 191 remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.15,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.15,en,,0,0,0,,You don't want me to be a policeman, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.75,en,,0,0,0,,Of course I do. I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:36.51,en,,0,0,0,,What do I have to show for all my time as a cop? Just enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.07,en,,0,0,0,,There you go! That means you've done your job well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.99,en,,0,0,0,,If a cop has no enemies, there can only be one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.55,en,,0,0,0,,He hasn't caught any crooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.91,en,,0,0,0,,I'm glad they're out to frighten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:48.75,en,,0,0,0,,It proves you're a tough, good cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.19,en,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.75,en,,0,0,0,,But I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.03,en,,0,0,0,,I resigned today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:56.87,en,,0,0,0,,-Really? -Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.14,en,,0,0,0,,You're really quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.51,en,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.87,en,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.31,en,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.75,en,,0,0,0,,May, all these years I haven't treated you as well as I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:14.19,en,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:17.27,en,,0,0,0,,I have three month's holiday. Let's go somewhere else to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:20.59,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, you really mean it? Where to, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.47,en,,0,0,0,,-Bali. -Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.71,en,,0,0,0,,We haven't travelled in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.71,en,,0,0,0,,Right, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.10,en,,0,0,0,,It always feels good to fly on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.62,en,,0,0,0,,-That'll be $5,540, please. -Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.95,en,,0,0,0,,191 see you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.43,en,,0,0,0,,-Credit card? -Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.27,en,,0,0,0,,Here's our catalogue, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.67,en,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.35,en,,0,0,0,,What clothes should I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:05.19,en,,0,0,0,,You won't need any in Bali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:06.91,en,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:09.03,en,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.75,en,,0,0,0,,I just hope they don't rip us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.55,en,,0,0,0,,They're a big company. They're trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.91,en,,0,0,0,,Well, it's paid for now. Let's cross our fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.27,en,,0,0,0,,-Fay! -Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:22.03,en,,0,0,0,,-Long time no see! Is this your area? -Yes. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:24.15,en,,0,0,0,,We've received a bomb threat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:27.63,en,,0,0,0,,-Really? -Yeah. Can you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:31.87,en,,0,0,0,,-All right, then. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:33.15,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:35.23,en,,0,0,0,,I'll just take a look, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:37.31,en,,0,0,0,,Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:38.54,en,,0,0,0,,Just in time. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.43,en,,0,0,0,,We got a call about a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:42.94,en,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:45.95,en,,0,0,0,,I don't think the guy was kidding. He told us to clear the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.71,en,,0,0,0,,We have ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:48.87,en,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.83,en,,0,0,0,,The manager said he's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:54.35,en,,0,0,0,,Start clearing the building now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:56.74,en,,0,0,0,,There are too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.83,en,,0,0,0,,If it's a hoax, who'll be to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:00.87,en,,0,0,0,,I'm used to getting an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.42,en,,0,0,0,,If it is real, we'll endanger lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:05.35,en,,0,0,0,,That's true. What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:07.07,en,,0,0,0,,Consider it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:09.31,en,,0,0,0,,Clear the building. Call headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:10.59,en,,0,0,0,,Where's the fire alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:12.75,en,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.27,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.51,en,,0,0,0,,We're gonna set off the fire alarm. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:24.23,en,,0,0,0,,-Your baton. -But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:25.63,en,,0,0,0,,Come on! 191 take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.35,en,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:44.63,en,,0,0,0,,Don't panic. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:47.71,en,,0,0,0,,Come back. I've opened the till already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.31,en,,0,0,0,,Have they paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:52.63,en,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:58.50,en,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:01.51,en,,0,0,0,,What should we do? They're not taking any notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:02.51,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:07.39,en,,0,0,0,,Don't stay here. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:09.03,en,,0,0,0,,Your attention please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.03,en,,0,0,0,,Evacuate the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:14.03,en,,0,0,0,,Everybody please leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:16.35,en,,0,0,0,,There's afire in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.44,0:24:18.43,en,,0,0,0,,Please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:22.55,en,,0,0,0,,Please leave in an orderly manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:24.79,en,,0,0,0,,Everybody outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:26.10,en,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:35.43,en,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Why is the alarm on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:37.99,en,,0,0,0,,What about our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:40.63,en,,0,0,0,,-Fay. -What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.79,en,,0,0,0,,Get them out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.60,0:24:47.43,en,,0,0,0,,This is for your own safety. Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:49.27,en,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.36,0:24:51.19,en,,0,0,0,,I won't be long. You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.44,0:24:56.71,en,,0,0,0,,Check the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.52,0:25:14.87,en,,0,0,0,,I can't understand this. It's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.84,0:25:22.59,en,,0,0,0,,-Who's in charge? -You talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:26.43,en,,0,0,0,,Please leave now. The police will take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:29.03,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui. Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.12,0:25:31.91,en,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. You go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.36,0:25:38.63,en,,0,0,0,,Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.72,0:25:39.75,en,,0,0,0,,Who made the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.84,0:25:43.54,en,,0,0,0,,We received a bomb threat, but we didn't know if it was a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.24,0:25:45.67,en,,0,0,0,,Who set off the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.36,0:25:48.55,en,,0,0,0,,It was me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.64,0:25:50.95,en,,0,0,0,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.04,0:25:57.59,en,,0,0,0,,Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.72,0:25:59.83,en,,0,0,0,,Sir, when I was in the Police Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.92,0:26:03.75,en,,0,0,0,,I was taught that public safety comes first,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.84,0:26:04.79,en,,0,0,0,,so I set off the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.92,0:26:06.71,en,,0,0,0,,Do you think you're indispensable?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.16,0:26:11.86,en,,0,0,0,,Superintendent, there's no fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.96,0:26:14.83,en,,0,0,0,,but your men cleared the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.92,0:26:17.22,en,,0,0,0,,Right. The Bomb Disposal Unit is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.32,0:26:18.99,en,,0,0,0,,You won't be needed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.08,0:26:21.23,en,,0,0,0,,Right. I hope this isn't a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.32,0:26:22.99,en,,0,0,0,,So do I, Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.08,0:26:25.51,en,,0,0,0,,Raymond, they want to see the head man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.60,0:26:27.39,en,,0,0,0,,Shall I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.52,0:26:30.15,en,,0,0,0,,-Where's the Bomb Disposal Unit? -On their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.00,0:26:35.03,en,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.12,0:26:36.75,en,,0,0,0,,Did I do the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.84,0:26:39.30,en,,0,0,0,,How do I do know? Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.40,0:26:43.31,en,,0,0,0,,Right now, we have to wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:45.55,en,,0,0,0,,Tell them to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.64,0:26:47.35,en,,0,0,0,,You can go back in very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.72,0:26:49.91,en,,0,0,0,,My ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.28,0:27:14.23,en,,0,0,0,,When can we go back in?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.36,0:27:16.07,en,,0,0,0,,-Now what? -Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.16,0:27:18.11,en,,0,0,0,,-Here's your ball, kiddo. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.68,0:27:25.63,en,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:27.91,en,,0,0,0,,The Bomb Disposal Unit is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.04,0:27:32.63,en,,0,0,0,,If they don't find anything, the boss will blow a fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.72,0:27:34.55,en,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bill, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.64,0:27:36.15,en,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.04,0:27:52.15,en,,0,0,0,,Red alert! All units move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.32,0:27:54.62,en,,0,0,0,,Go and fight the fire. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.92,0:28:08.35,en,,0,0,0,,I suppose the good news is nobody got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.44,0:28:10.07,en,,0,0,0,,What are the losses?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.16,0:28:12.03,en,,0,0,0,,The insurance will cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.12,0:28:14.95,en,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about the damage to our image.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.04,0:28:18.79,en,,0,0,0,,I've asked the press to cooperate, and I'm sure they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:22.03,en,,0,0,0,,But who did it? And why our company?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.12,0:28:24.19,en,,0,0,0,,It may not be against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.28,0:28:26.63,en,,0,0,0,,It could be someone who's mentally disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:30.67,en,,0,0,0,,There's a man on the line, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.76,0:28:33.87,en,,0,0,0,,-He says he planted the bomb. -Have it put through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.84,0:28:36.39,en,,0,0,0,,Put him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.64,0:28:38.71,en,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:41.23,en,,0,0,0,,Listen, we planted the bomb in your shopping centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.32,0:28:43.70,en,,0,0,0,,We want$10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:46.51,en,,0,0,0,,Pay up or your other properties will get bombed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:47.74,en,,0,0,0,,Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.84,0:28:49.39,en,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.48,0:28:52.55,en,,0,0,0,,But it's a huge amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.64,0:28:54.39,en,,0,0,0,,We91 need to call a board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:57.43,en,,0,0,0,,You've got 24 hours. And don't call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.16,0:29:02.67,en,,0,0,0,,-What do we do, then? -Must be some kind of hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.84,0:29:05.27,en,,0,0,0,,Yes. So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.40,0:29:06.43,en,,0,0,0,,Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.52,0:29:09.27,en,,0,0,0,,We pay enough taxes. The police should do something for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.68,0:29:12.55,en,,0,0,0,,-Get me through to the chief. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.68,0:29:14.91,en,,0,0,0,,Raymond, you were extremely lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.00,0:29:18.47,en,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that no-one was hurt in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.56,0:29:20.83,en,,0,0,0,,Thank God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.16,0:29:23.27,en,,0,0,0,,And the Chu case... well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:26.43,en,,0,0,0,,-Thank you. But it wasn't just me. -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.52,0:29:28.15,en,,0,0,0,,You've proven yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.24,0:29:32.02,en,,0,0,0,,You should handle this case. Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.12,0:29:33.59,en,,0,0,0,,-Sure. -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.28,0:29:39.11,en,,0,0,0,,This is a very tough case.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.20,0:29:41.39,en,,0,0,0,,That's why they gave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:45.23,en,,0,0,0,,Who in our department do you think can solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.32,0:29:46.95,en,,0,0,0,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.04,0:29:48.71,en,,0,0,0,,I want a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.80,0:29:50.99,en,,0,0,0,,It's definitely not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:55.35,en,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could bring back somebody who's on leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:57.03,en,,0,0,0,,Do you mean somebody like Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.12,0:29:58.59,en,,0,0,0,,He has substantial experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.68,0:29:59.87,en,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.96,0:30:02.11,en,,0,0,0,,He's unorthodox, impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.20,0:30:04.43,en,,0,0,0,,He'll only give us trouble. We have to bear the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.52,0:30:08.43,en,,0,0,0,,I agree he's a little bit rash, but underneath he's a good cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.52,0:30:09.58,en,,0,0,0,,I won't let him do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.68,0:30:12.67,en,,0,0,0,,But if you think he's our man, you go and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.76,0:30:21.67,en,,0,0,0,,Let's see who's the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.20,0:30:34.23,en,,0,0,0,,-Over there. -Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:44.99,en,,0,0,0,,Fasten your seat belt, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.08,0:30:46.67,en,,0,0,0,,I forgot the sunscreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.76,0:30:47.95,en,,0,0,0,,Buy it when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:52.59,en,,0,0,0,,Did you get your passport when you were younger?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:55.55,en,,0,0,0,,Put out a call for Detective Chan Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:56.62,en,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.32,0:30:59.59,en,,0,0,0,,Your attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.68,0:31:01.31,en,,0,0,0,,Will Chan Ka Kui...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.40,0:31:02.87,en,,0,0,0,,Let me see. No, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.96,0:31:05.15,en,,0,0,0,,-It's cute. -It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.24,0:31:07.11,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui please contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.20,0:31:08.15,en,,0,0,0,,That's you. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.24,0:31:09.83,en,,0,0,0,,-What's up? -I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.92,0:31:11.39,en,,0,0,0,,I won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.36,0:31:15.79,en,,0,0,0,,-Are you Mr. Chan? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.88,0:31:19.83,en,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid there seems to be a problem with your passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.92,0:31:21.11,en,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.20,0:31:22.55,en,,0,0,0,,It'll just be a quick check.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:25.03,en,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:27.99,en,,0,0,0,,I'll be back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.12,0:31:29.31,en,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.44,0:31:30.71,en,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.32,0:31:33.30,en,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.12,0:31:47.55,en,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.64,0:31:49.63,en,,0,0,0,,-Thank you. -You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:51.19,en,,0,0,0,,What is it? I have a plane waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.28,0:31:52.95,en,,0,0,0,,We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.04,0:31:56.91,en,,0,0,0,,It seems that the bombing case has become a blackmail case,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:58.35,en,,0,0,0,,and it's a very tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.44,0:32:01.43,en,,0,0,0,,-So? -This case is a real challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:03.82,en,,0,0,0,,Raymond was hoping...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.92,0:32:07.15,en,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that you might cancel your holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.24,0:32:09.62,en,,0,0,0,,No! I've already boarded the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.72,0:32:11.03,en,,0,0,0,,Plus, I've quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.16,0:32:12.43,en,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.52,0:32:14.75,en,,0,0,0,,You've been under a lot of pressure lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.84,0:32:17.22,en,,0,0,0,,-But ducking out like this? -I'm not ducking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.36,0:32:19.92,en,,0,0,0,,He said he's not ducking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.08,0:32:25.39,en,,0,0,0,,Raymond is a great admirer of your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.52,0:32:29.55,en,,0,0,0,,I don't have any abilities. I'm too impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.64,0:32:32.23,en,,0,0,0,,Impulsive? More like... a man of action!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:34.88,en,,0,0,0,,If only I could control my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.00,0:32:38.35,en,,0,0,0,,A true man of action acts on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.44,0:32:41.67,en,,0,0,0,,I think the police force needs men with discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.80,0:32:43.95,en,,0,0,0,,Instinctive men have to be unconventional,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:46.39,en,,0,0,0,,even at the cost of discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.48,0:32:49.23,en,,0,0,0,,If you did everything by the book, no case would ever get solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.40,0:32:51.31,en,,0,0,0,,-Am I right? -Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:54.83,en,,0,0,0,,I'd better get back on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.84,0:32:58.27,en,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.36,0:33:00.03,en,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.32,0:33:05.54,en,,0,0,0,,How much is the ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:08.23,en,,0,0,0,,Ten million. That's all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.32,0:33:10.91,en,,0,0,0,,-Do we have any suspects? -Not a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.00,0:33:13.56,en,,0,0,0,,Do you think these people are insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:15.83,en,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.96,0:33:19.19,en,,0,0,0,,Have you traced the dynamite?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:21.70,en,,0,0,0,,-Why? -Yes, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.80,0:33:25.07,en,,0,0,0,,Simple. Dynamite is a controlled substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.16,0:33:30.07,en,,0,0,0,,You either smuggle it in or you steal it from a local company.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.16,0:33:32.83,en,,0,0,0,,He's right. We hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:36.83,en,,0,0,0,,We must find their bomb factory before the company pays the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.92,0:33:39.38,en,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we can foil their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.48,0:33:42.19,en,,0,0,0,,How is it you always solve problems so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.28,0:33:44.43,en,,0,0,0,,You're made for this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.52,0:33:45.50,en,,0,0,0,,You're in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.36,0:33:49.71,en,,0,0,0,,I've got a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:51.55,en,,0,0,0,,Wait! Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.60,0:33:56.95,en,,0,0,0,,You can go there anytime. This case is once-in-a-lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.04,0:33:58.71,en,,0,0,0,,Go there next time. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:01.79,en,,0,0,0,,I'd better talk to May first.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.88,0:34:03.23,en,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.08,0:34:09.47,en,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:11.91,en,,0,0,0,,-Miss! -Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.00,0:34:13.63,en,,0,0,0,,-My plane... -It just took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.84,0:34:18.35,en,,0,0,0,,It's taken off!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.44,0:34:20.11,en,,0,0,0,,You've missed your flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:23.43,en,,0,0,0,,Count on them to stay on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.52,0:34:25.43,en,,0,0,0,,I still have May's passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.52,0:34:29.30,en,,0,0,0,,Damn! It sure isn't your lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.16,0:34:32.38,en,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.88,0:34:44.35,en,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bill, we'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.68,0:34:48.14,en,,0,0,0,,-You all right? -I ate something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.00,0:34:52.19,en,,0,0,0,,-That way, sir. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.28,0:34:56.31,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. We're police officers. We're here to see Mr. Fung.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.40,0:34:58.39,en,,0,0,0,,-30th floor. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.68,0:35:01.95,en,,0,0,0,,Bugging devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.24,0:35:05.54,en,,0,0,0,,A bug? Look out... Nixon lost his job because of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.64,0:35:09.39,en,,0,0,0,,If we want to solve the case, we have to know our targets well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.48,0:35:11.99,en,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you. Put them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.32,0:35:16.75,en,,0,0,0,,Miss Wong, there are two police officers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:19.47,en,,0,0,0,,-Where's the bathroom? -On your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.56,0:35:20.99,en,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.16,0:35:24.67,en,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:27.31,en,,0,0,0,,Twenty-four, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.12,0:35:30.10,en,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.56,0:35:35.07,en,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bill, I'm really worried about May.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.16,0:35:38.15,en,,0,0,0,,I'll call Jakarta Airport as soon as I get back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.20,0:35:48.47,en,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.60,0:36:04.07,en,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed of yourself. Haven't you got any manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.12,0:36:11.19,en,,0,0,0,,Let's use the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.08,0:36:26.19,en,,0,0,0,,Detective Chan to see Miss Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.28,0:36:28.07,en,,0,0,0,,-Please wait. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.64,0:36:34.35,en,,0,0,0,,-Ka Kui. -Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:38.95,en,,0,0,0,,I figured you were used to taking the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.04,0:36:40.63,en,,0,0,0,,That's no excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.76,0:36:42.47,en,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.60,0:36:45.19,en,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Chang. This is Detective Chan. We...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.32,0:36:47.27,en,,0,0,0,,-Please come with me. -We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.36,0:36:51.55,en,,0,0,0,,I know. Mr. Fung is busy now, but he's signed the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.20,0:36:59.31,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.80,0:37:07.03,en,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me, where's the toilet? -Down the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.04,0:37:09.07,en,,0,0,0,,Here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.68,0:37:10.66,en,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.88,0:37:16.03,en,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Where's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.16,0:37:17.43,en,,0,0,0,,He had a sudden urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.12,0:37:35.11,en,,0,0,0,,There's the chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.24,0:37:36.51,en,,0,0,0,,That site is worth three billion. There would be a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:38.03,en,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.16,0:37:40.11,en,,0,0,0,,-Detective Chan is here. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.24,0:37:41.51,en,,0,0,0,,Than ks for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.68,0:37:47.67,en,,0,0,0,,You're developing the new properties very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.44,0:38:00.42,en,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.52,0:38:07.03,en,,0,0,0,,Directors, managers, and department heads, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.12,0:38:10.03,en,,0,0,0,,I've called this meeting to review the performance
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.12,0:38:12.55,en,,0,0,0,,of our property portfolio over the last six months,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.64,0:38:15.75,en,,0,0,0,,and to set the sales target for the next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.24,0:38:21.55,en,,0,0,0,,You may all know that since the stock market collapse last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.64,0:38:25.55,en,,0,0,0,,the Hang Seng Index has risen 66%.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.64,0:38:30.23,en,,0,0,0,,Let me show you the performance of the major blue chip shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:55.59,en,,0,0,0,,However, given the performance of the bank and property sectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:39:01.23,en,,0,0,0,,the outlook of the stock market for the next six months remains uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.32,0:39:03.27,en,,0,0,0,,In situations like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.40,0:39:07.83,en,,0,0,0,,small investors are likely to put their money in property.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.76,0:39:25.54,en,,0,0,0,,So we have to accelerate the pace of our new housing developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.52,0:39:31.95,en,,0,0,0,,Hi, gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.56,0:39:45.99,en,,0,0,0,,If someone asks the chairman for this, it's$500 to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.12,0:39:47.47,en,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.60,0:39:48.51,en,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.40,0:39:51.63,en,,0,0,0,,-What happened? -It's a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.72,0:39:54.10,en,,0,0,0,,-Did you plant the bugs? -Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.20,0:39:56.11,en,,0,0,0,,-And the desk? -All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.20,0:39:58.50,en,,0,0,0,,-Was it easy? -He wasn't against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.36,0:40:03.43,en,,0,0,0,,-What did they say? -Something about houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.52,0:40:04.47,en,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.56,0:40:06.55,en,,0,0,0,,-Where are you going? -191 take the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.72,0:40:32.23,en,,0,0,0,,May's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.60,0:40:39.43,en,,0,0,0,,May, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.56,0:40:40.78,en,,0,0,0,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.92,0:40:42.35,en,,0,0,0,,You scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:43.95,en,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.60,0:40:47.67,en,,0,0,0,,You... you didn't want me to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.76,0:40:51.35,en,,0,0,0,,You left me there and took my passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.44,0:40:54.15,en,,0,0,0,,When I got there, I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.24,0:40:59.18,en,,0,0,0,,Before I was sent back here, they detained me for ten hours in a cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.28,0:41:01.63,en,,0,0,0,,Why should I keep my voice down?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.72,0:41:07.23,en,,0,0,0,,When you take your dog for a walk, do you not take him home afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:08.91,en,,0,0,0,,I'm even worse than a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:10.59,en,,0,0,0,,May, they're watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.68,0:41:13.39,en,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.48,0:41:15.86,en,,0,0,0,,This is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.96,0:41:20.35,en,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me in front of everyone what you think I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.44,0:41:21.91,en,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you take me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.04,0:41:23.83,en,,0,0,0,,You're my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.96,0:41:25.59,en,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.68,0:41:27.63,en,,0,0,0,,Open up! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:34.79,en,,0,0,0,,If that's true, why do you treat me this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.88,0:41:37.34,en,,0,0,0,,You treat strangers better than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.44,0:41:38.95,en,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.08,0:41:43.03,en,,0,0,0,,...it's over between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.72,0:41:59.23,en,,0,0,0,,Chan Ka Kui, I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.80,0:42:04.36,en,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bill, did you make that call?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.44,0:42:06.27,en,,0,0,0,,I had to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.36,0:42:08.11,en,,0,0,0,,You've ruined my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.64,0:42:21.62,en,,0,0,0,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.72,0:42:24.10,en,,0,0,0,,Go away or I'll run you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.20,0:42:26.39,en,,0,0,0,,-Go away! -Don't be childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.92,0:42:32.07,en,,0,0,0,,Don't grab my bag! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.20,0:42:34.83,en,,0,0,0,,Don't even touch me. Go away. Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.96,0:42:36.51,en,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.64,0:42:38.63,en,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.72,0:42:40.91,en,,0,0,0,,I've nothing else to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.04,0:42:42.55,en,,0,0,0,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.16,0:42:46.30,en,,0,0,0,,May, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.04,0:42:50.71,en,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me. Don't touch my motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.80,0:42:52.63,en,,0,0,0,,Keep away. I don't want you anywhere near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.72,0:42:54.47,en,,0,0,0,,-Let me explain. -Keep away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.92,0:42:58.99,en,,0,0,0,,Why won't you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.32,0:43:04.99,en,,0,0,0,,Just keep away from me. I never want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.64,0:43:07.83,en,,0,0,0,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.96,0:43:10.34,en,,0,0,0,,All right, get back to work. I want to see Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.48,0:43:13.11,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, the boss wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.16,0:43:27.79,en,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.92,0:43:28.83,en,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.96,0:43:30.79,en,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to call May to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.92,0:43:32.35,en,,0,0,0,,I don't think it would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.48,0:43:35.27,en,,0,0,0,,Don't explain anything to women! This is my way to handle ¡®em...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.36,0:43:38.27,en,,0,0,0,,if a man's not at home, it's obvious he's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.36,0:43:40.92,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I have to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.00,0:43:44.31,en,,0,0,0,,Don't pay any attention to his chauvinism. Go and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.28,0:44:13.75,en,,0,0,0,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.32,0:44:20.91,en,,0,0,0,,It's better than wasting my time here. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.04,0:44:22.39,en,,0,0,0,,Can I walk you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.40,0:44:24.38,en,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.16,0:44:31.91,en,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:33.26,en,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.84,0:44:36.19,en,,0,0,0,,Get me, it's me you want. Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.36,0:44:39.83,en,,0,0,0,,-You're in this together. -Don't try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.96,0:44:43.31,en,,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.28,0:44:50.90,en,,0,0,0,,I really had you going! I got the both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.24,0:44:54.27,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.40,0:45:07.38,en,,0,0,0,,I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.44,0:45:22.27,en,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.36,0:45:26.79,en,,0,0,0,,If I thought it was just a simple game, I wouldn't call my men to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.92,0:45:28.14,en,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.28,0:45:31.31,en,,0,0,0,,My boss asked me to teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.40,0:45:33.55,en,,0,0,0,,I'm getting paid to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.64,0:45:37.67,en,,0,0,0,,But I don't need to dirty my hands. My men can take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.76,0:45:38.95,en,,0,0,0,,Get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.08,0:45:41.15,en,,0,0,0,,We91 give you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.24,0:45:45.51,en,,0,0,0,,If you apologise to Mr. Ko now, we won't break both of your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.60,0:45:48.06,en,,0,0,0,,We'll just break one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.20,0:45:50.47,en,,0,0,0,,Cut the bullshit. Go on, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.64,0:45:52.67,en,,0,0,0,,Kill a cop? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.76,0:45:54.39,en,,0,0,0,,My boss wants to teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.52,0:45:57.67,en,,0,0,0,,Ripping a few limbs off should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.44,0:46:07.27,en,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.40,0:46:08.75,en,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.56,0:46:23.15,en,,0,0,0,,There he is. Beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.20,0:47:29.07,en,,0,0,0,,Go on, finish him off. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.68,0:48:32.55,en,,0,0,0,,Move over. Let me drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.56,0:48:45.31,en,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into mashed banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.64,0:49:02.99,en,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my fault! I was paid to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.28,0:49:28.84,en,,0,0,0,,Keep away or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.92,0:49:29.87,en,,0,0,0,,Shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.00,0:49:31.39,en,,0,0,0,,-191 shoot. -Shoot here!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.48,0:49:32.91,en,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.64,0:49:43.23,en,,0,0,0,,It's not. It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.32,0:49:44.83,en,,0,0,0,,Next time 191 kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.96,0:49:47.52,en,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.52,0:49:56.71,en,,0,0,0,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.80,0:49:58.75,en,,0,0,0,,Did they hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.84,0:50:00.15,en,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.32,0:50:02.83,en,,0,0,0,,You'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:08.15,en,,0,0,0,,Why did you chase him? That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.24,0:50:10.43,en,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make things up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.56,0:50:13.79,en,,0,0,0,,If it had been acid in that pistol and not ink...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.16,0:50:16.63,en,,0,0,0,,I'd be scarred for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.24,0:50:19.51,en,,0,0,0,,Maybe they wanted to distract you and then kidnap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.20,0:50:22.51,en,,0,0,0,,Then what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.20,0:50:30.03,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, I want my boyfriend to be gentle, not a savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.08,0:50:32.91,en,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.12,0:50:43.26,en,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.88,0:50:52.55,en,,0,0,0,,"Police Detective in Park Rumpus." Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.64,0:50:53.86,en,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.40,0:50:58.59,en,,0,0,0,,191 check out the surveillance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.44,0:51:07.83,en,,0,0,0,,ACTIVE-DUTY POLICEMAN INVOLVED IN 10-MAN PARK BRAWL
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.44,0:51:11.07,en,,0,0,0,,It was me. Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.88,0:51:18.71,en,,0,0,0,,I know Chu wants revenge, but don't take the law into your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.84,0:51:20.03,en,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.60,0:51:22.47,en,,0,0,0,,Anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.60,0:51:24.90,en,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.00,0:51:26.75,en,,0,0,0,,I can cope with it. I just want them to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.84,0:51:29.87,en,,0,0,0,,All right. But keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.88,0:51:32.79,en,,0,0,0,,Now we've got a surveillance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.88,0:51:36.31,en,,0,0,0,,They're very good. Go and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.64,0:51:46.47,en,,0,0,0,,Did he give you an earful? Did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.56,0:51:48.70,en,,0,0,0,,Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.84,0:51:53.15,en,,0,0,0,,He just wants to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.24,0:51:55.23,en,,0,0,0,,How can somebody show off if they don't have an audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.80,0:52:12.19,en,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.32,0:52:13.71,en,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.80,0:52:16.67,en,,0,0,0,,This is Detective Chan Ka Kui. Detective Ng, Detective Mui.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.60,0:52:18.58,en,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.72,0:52:21.28,en,,0,0,0,,You guys introduce yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.40,0:52:23.91,en,,0,0,0,,This is the Special Tactical Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.00,0:52:25.27,en,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.36,0:52:28.07,en,,0,0,0,,They have great expertise in tracking targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.20,0:52:31.19,en,,0,0,0,,But why? Will this be useful for the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.28,0:52:33.71,en,,0,0,0,,Because we don't even know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.80,0:52:35.15,en,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.24,0:52:37.83,en,,0,0,0,,Follow anyone suspicious, and then you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.92,0:52:38.87,en,,0,0,0,,Follow the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.96,0:52:42.19,en,,0,0,0,,Then we can find the their hiding place for making bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.28,0:52:45.31,en,,0,0,0,,We could follow them during the transaction, then arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.44,0:52:47.35,en,,0,0,0,,-That simple? -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.48,0:52:49.94,en,,0,0,0,,Good. That's why I always have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.04,0:52:51.47,en,,0,0,0,,Hope you have a smooth collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.56,0:52:53.23,en,,0,0,0,,Detective Ng, could I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.12,0:52:56.59,en,,0,0,0,,There will be room for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.68,0:52:57.66,en,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.76,0:52:59.03,en,,0,0,0,,-Bye. -Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.80,0:53:03.43,en,,0,0,0,,-Detective Chan. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.56,0:53:05.47,en,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.88,0:53:10.34,en,,0,0,0,,You guys are cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.32,0:53:19.71,en,,0,0,0,,Anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.88,0:53:23.31,en,,0,0,0,,Fung said his shares would go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.44,0:53:25.47,en,,0,0,0,,That's hardly relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.56,0:53:28.75,en,,0,0,0,,And his girlfriend is a supermodel!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.84,0:53:30.23,en,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.36,0:53:32.92,en,,0,0,0,,191 take it. You go and call May.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.68,0:53:35.47,en,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.12,0:53:44.67,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.44,0:53:50.47,en,,0,0,0,,Your conditions have been presented to the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.60,0:53:51.82,en,,0,0,0,,and they have agreed to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.92,0:53:53.91,en,,0,0,0,,No shit. Do you have the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.08,0:53:57.99,en,,0,0,0,,We don't have it all. $10 million is a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.12,0:53:59.43,en,,0,0,0,,Trace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.56,0:54:07.54,en,,0,0,0,,It's from Tai Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.72,0:54:08.83,en,,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.84,0:54:30.43,en,,0,0,0,,He's on Ting Kok Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.44,0:54:35.83,en,,0,0,0,,HQ, calling all foot patrols. Are there any units on Ting Kok Road, over?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.28,0:54:41.84,en,,0,0,0,,This is PC 12674 on Ting Kok Road, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.96,0:54:44.03,en,,0,0,0,,PC 12674,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.12,0:54:45.91,en,,0,0,0,,check anybody leaving a phone box in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.32,0:54:50.71,en,,0,0,0,,Are you stalling for time?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.84,0:54:52.99,en,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.12,0:54:54.71,en,,0,0,0,,Now we want 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.84,0:54:58.27,en,,0,0,0,,Twenty million! Such a huge sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.44,0:55:00.11,en,,0,0,0,,Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.24,0:55:01.15,en,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.32,0:55:11.51,en,,0,0,0,,This is PC 12674.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.60,0:55:12.55,en,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.64,0:55:14.27,en,,0,0,0,,I think I've got a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.40,0:55:16.11,en,,0,0,0,,Be careful. He's very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.20,0:55:18.03,en,,0,0,0,,He could be armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.16,0:55:19.75,en,,0,0,0,,Keep everything low key.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.12,0:55:32.79,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. You're supposed to use the pedestrian crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.00,0:55:36.67,en,,0,0,0,,-Move along. -Give me a chance, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.80,0:55:38.31,en,,0,0,0,,Can I see your ID card?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.68,0:55:52.03,en,,0,0,0,,Calling HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.36,0:55:57.59,en,,0,0,0,,PC 12674, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.52,0:56:14.30,en,,0,0,0,,An officer needs assistance on Ting Kok Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.88,0:56:19.79,en,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, he isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.88,0:56:21.79,en,,0,0,0,,Don't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.88,0:56:24.23,en,,0,0,0,,That's the way things go. It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.72,0:56:27.11,en,,0,0,0,,How long have you been in uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.20,0:56:28.63,en,,0,0,0,,About two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.00,0:56:31.27,en,,0,0,0,,Then you're excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.36,0:56:34.43,en,,0,0,0,,Will I get in trouble for losing my gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.52,0:56:35.66,en,,0,0,0,,What about promotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.76,0:56:36.90,en,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.00,0:56:41.31,en,,0,0,0,,As long as you learn from the experience, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.40,0:56:43.47,en,,0,0,0,,-It happens to every cop. -It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.56,0:56:45.11,en,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'd recognise him?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.20,0:56:46.23,en,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.32,0:56:47.83,en,,0,0,0,,Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.92,0:56:49.79,en,,0,0,0,,I could do with someone like you on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.88,0:56:50.86,en,,0,0,0,,I'll see to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.24,0:56:55.23,en,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Can you file this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.76,0:56:58.55,en,,0,0,0,,-Hello. -It's Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.64,0:57:00.03,en,,0,0,0,,-Go ahead. -News.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.12,0:57:01.10,en,,0,0,0,,What news?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.20,0:57:03.15,en,,0,0,0,,A guy called Crazy Fai sells dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.24,0:57:05.23,en,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock, Hoi Wong Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.20,0:57:22.63,en,,0,0,0,,-Do you know what we'll do next? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.76,0:57:24.27,en,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.60,0:57:33.19,en,,0,0,0,,-What do you want? -Are you Fai? I want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.28,0:57:34.11,en,,0,0,0,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.24,0:57:35.75,en,,0,0,0,,No, but you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.80,0:57:40.43,en,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.56,0:57:41.87,en,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.12,0:57:49.03,en,,0,0,0,,-What's your name? -Lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.12,0:57:50.34,en,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.44,0:57:52.31,en,,0,0,0,,Some explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.40,0:57:53.35,en,,0,0,0,,Explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.48,0:57:54.91,en,,0,0,0,,Do you have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.04,0:57:56.79,en,,0,0,0,,-What are they for? -Fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.76,0:58:00.59,en,,0,0,0,,You don't look like a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.68,0:58:02.59,en,,0,0,0,,What if I told you it was for business?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.68,0:58:05.95,en,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a good price. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.56,0:58:11.15,en,,0,0,0,,All right.., but I need to speak to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.24,0:58:13.15,en,,0,0,0,,It's not my stuff. Don't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.24,0:58:14.07,en,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.16,0:58:39.67,en,,0,0,0,,Sorry, he's out of stock, but he'll call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:42.83,en,,0,0,0,,Stay here, I'll be back when I've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:43.90,en,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.76,0:59:30.63,en,,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.24,0:59:33.22,en,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.36,0:59:35.47,en,,0,0,0,,CID. On your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.08,0:59:47.91,en,,0,0,0,,Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.04,0:59:50.19,en,,0,0,0,,-I only came here for a drink. -A drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.28,0:59:51.99,en,,0,0,0,,We heard you were dealing contraband.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.44,0:59:56.55,en,,0,0,0,,Eyes front.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.80,1:00:06.51,en,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.64,1:00:08.39,en,,0,0,0,,Throw me your gun. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.84,1:00:14.19,en,,0,0,0,,Stand over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.64,1:00:17.67,en,,0,0,0,,Easy. Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.64,1:00:31.07,en,,0,0,0,,Come on. Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.16,1:00:32.67,en,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.44,1:01:36.42,en,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.60,1:01:40.03,en,,0,0,0,,You screwed me over, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.16,1:01:41.55,en,,0,0,0,,Why did you call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.36,1:01:46.87,en,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.92,1:01:52.67,en,,0,0,0,,Please, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.76,1:01:54.75,en,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.28,1:01:56.47,en,,0,0,0,,Why did you double-cross me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.60,1:01:58.59,en,,0,0,0,,To make sure you weren't a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.68,1:02:00.75,en,,0,0,0,,That's why I called the cops, to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.84,1:02:01.98,en,,0,0,0,,I can get what you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.12,1:02:03.15,en,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.32,1:02:05.19,en,,0,0,0,,Have you got the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.96,1:02:11.87,en,,0,0,0,,It's cash on delivery.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.48,1:02:16.79,en,,0,0,0,,Keep a lookout.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.04,1:02:33.18,en,,0,0,0,,Is it good stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.28,1:02:35.07,en,,0,0,0,,It's from the quarries.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.16,1:02:36.14,en,,0,0,0,,Got any more?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.28,1:02:37.71,en,,0,0,0,,Yeah, plenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.92,1:02:47.55,en,,0,0,0,,There's enough to blow up the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.88,1:02:52.31,en,,0,0,0,,I just met him! I've never seen him before!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.92,1:02:57.43,en,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can get away?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.60,1:03:01.07,en,,0,0,0,,Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.16,1:03:02.47,en,,0,0,0,,A cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.00,1:03:10.43,en,,0,0,0,,Two spoons of sugar?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.56,1:03:11.51,en,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.92,1:03:14.31,en,,0,0,0,,The temperature okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.32,1:03:19.79,en,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.92,1:03:23.03,en,,0,0,0,,This is stretching the law. If I were him, I'd clam up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.00,1:03:26.79,en,,0,0,0,,You seem comfortable. Will you cooperate with us now?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.76,1:03:29.11,en,,0,0,0,,Cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.24,1:03:30.22,en,,0,0,0,,You want me to die?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.36,1:03:32.55,en,,0,0,0,,If you cooperate, you can walk out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.64,1:03:34.07,en,,0,0,0,,We91 keep everything secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.16,1:03:36.83,en,,0,0,0,,If need be, we'll keep you under protection.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.92,1:03:39.75,en,,0,0,0,,If you three could protect me the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.84,1:03:41.23,en,,0,0,0,,then I would consider it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.40,1:03:45.91,en,,0,0,0,,Don't talk that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.00,1:03:47.79,en,,0,0,0,,Even if we were to release you now,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.88,1:03:52.51,en,,0,0,0,,we might, say, "find" drugs on you after you were gone,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.64,1:03:54.87,en,,0,0,0,,or maybe "discover" you've been molesting young girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.12,1:03:58.83,en,,0,0,0,,Does this get you good results?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.68,1:04:01.07,en,,0,0,0,,Sure. It never fails.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.04,1:04:07.42,en,,0,0,0,,What's the charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.52,1:04:09.98,en,,0,0,0,,I've seen a lot worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.96,1:04:12.71,en,,0,0,0,,191 play along before 191 go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.80,1:04:29.03,en,,0,0,0,,You all seem like nice young ladies!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.92,1:04:36.22,en,,0,0,0,,Have you not seen anything like this before?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.16,1:04:43.46,en,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.56,1:04:44.83,en,,0,0,0,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.36,1:04:48.83,en,,0,0,0,,Nice young ladies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.52,1:04:56.91,en,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to play along?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.08,1:04:58.59,en,,0,0,0,,I'll sue you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.96,1:05:01.51,en,,0,0,0,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.64,1:05:04.55,en,,0,0,0,,Guns have a way of going off when you least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.64,1:05:06.55,en,,0,0,0,,We91 just say it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.64,1:05:07.70,en,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Escaped prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.88,1:05:09.91,en,,0,0,0,,Escaped prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.00,1:05:12.23,en,,0,0,0,,No! 191 talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.36,1:05:15.47,en,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so? Come on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.56,1:05:17.35,en,,0,0,0,,-Cigarette? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.36,1:05:20.99,en,,0,0,0,,There are men in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.68,1:05:26.66,en,,0,0,0,,Show's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.36,1:05:31.07,en,,0,0,0,,I have sold three explosives lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.16,1:05:33.59,en,,0,0,0,,One buyer named Xing, he was a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.68,1:05:35.03,en,,0,0,0,,I've known him a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.16,1:05:36.99,en,,0,0,0,,He bought it to blast reef fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.12,1:05:40.63,en,,0,0,0,,The other guy buys my stuff to refill empty bullet shell cases
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.72,1:05:42.47,en,,0,0,0,,so he can sell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.56,1:05:44.11,en,,0,0,0,,But he's only bought a few.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.20,1:05:48.43,en,,0,0,0,,The third guy's name was Polar Bear. He's a big-time dealer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.52,1:05:50.87,en,,0,0,0,,He usually hangs out at the Yaumatei Pool Hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.44,1:06:16.63,en,,0,0,0,,Taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.96,1:06:24.75,en,,0,0,0,,Target's in a taxi. It's DP5608.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.88,1:06:26.39,en,,0,0,0,,Got it, Big Mouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.48,1:06:29.79,en,,0,0,0,,Taxi number DP5608, heading north to Kok Road.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.12,1:06:34.91,en,,0,0,0,,Copy, Big Mouth. I see target DP5608.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.20,1:06:44.19,en,,0,0,0,,It's headed to TST Metro Station.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.92,1:06:47.27,en,,0,0,0,,All copy. All copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.36,1:06:52.15,en,,0,0,0,,Renew info. Get to TST Metro Station.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.04,1:08:12.99,en,,0,0,0,,Target on metro heading to Kung Tong.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.76,1:08:15.07,en,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.48,1:08:19.59,en,,0,0,0,,-Stay there. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.12,1:08:52.79,en,,0,0,0,,Target off metro.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.48,1:09:38.99,en,,0,0,0,,Target in taxi CW721, heading to industrial area.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.48,1:09:48.19,en,,0,0,0,,Target out of the car, heading to Yat Sing Street.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.28,1:09:50.47,en,,0,0,0,,Copy. Over. Sun, your team leaves first.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.32,1:09:56.03,en,,0,0,0,,Car to Yat Sing Street.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.12,1:09:57.95,en,,0,0,0,,Start supervision. Wait for orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.04,1:09:59.18,en,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.68,1:10:11.03,en,,0,0,0,,191 take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.20,1:10:23.07,en,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, where is Pak Lok Street?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.16,1:10:24.67,en,,0,0,0,,-No idea. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.60,1:10:28.51,en,,0,0,0,,Someone carrying two bags heading your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.44,1:10:36.79,en,,0,0,0,,Polar Bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.36,1:10:39.95,en,,0,0,0,,You went shopping?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.04,1:10:41.99,en,,0,0,0,,Were you followed?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.08,1:10:43.30,en,,0,0,0,,No. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.88,1:10:47.02,en,,0,0,0,,Come on. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.12,1:10:48.39,en,,0,0,0,,There are three of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.40,1:11:02.11,en,,0,0,0,,Detective Chan, it's him. These must be the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.36,1:11:11.67,en,,0,0,0,,Three voices.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.68,1:11:21.35,en,,0,0,0,,Louder, let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.48,1:11:25.31,en,,0,0,0,,Brother, stop waiting!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.40,1:11:27.31,en,,0,0,0,,Everything ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.12,1:11:31.11,en,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.64,1:11:33.79,en,,0,0,0,,Then I have to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.12,1:11:48.43,en,,0,0,0,,Not here. Make sure we're not being bugged.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.52,1:11:51.75,en,,0,0,0,,Find a place at the TST. Make sure everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.84,1:11:53.15,en,,0,0,0,,Don't waste time. Get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.92,1:12:08.35,en,,0,0,0,,Three people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.40,1:12:13.51,en,,0,0,0,,-They're coming out. -Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.00,1:12:16.30,en,,0,0,0,,-You don't deserve this. -You don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.28,1:12:35.87,en,,0,0,0,,Check the plates and follow the van.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.68,1:12:38.87,en,,0,0,0,,You stay here. 191 go and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.72,1:12:45.28,en,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.72,1:12:51.91,en,,0,0,0,,We're starting the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.04,1:13:33.99,en,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.68,1:13:36.63,en,,0,0,0,,-Where are you going? -To take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.72,1:13:38.71,en,,0,0,0,,-Be careful. -I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.84,1:13:39.90,en,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.56,1:13:43.51,en,,0,0,0,,Detective Chan, they've shaken off our unit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.60,1:13:46.87,en,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, they'll come back. Call them off.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.44,1:13:49.63,en,,0,0,0,,Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.20,1:15:37.75,en,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.84,1:15:38.82,en,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.88,1:15:45.86,en,,0,0,0,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.96,1:15:47.59,en,,0,0,0,,-I fell over. -Someone's up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.52,1:16:07.11,en,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.76,1:16:10.95,en,,0,0,0,,Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.60,1:16:17.27,en,,0,0,0,,Police! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.36,1:16:22.74,en,,0,0,0,,This guy must be deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.84,1:16:27.91,en,,0,0,0,,Did you see three men come through here a few hours ago?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.76,1:16:36.39,en,,0,0,0,,You ask him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.16,1:16:43.59,en,,0,0,0,,Do you work here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.00,1:16:49.91,en,,0,0,0,,Do you sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.92,1:16:57.95,en,,0,0,0,,Right. I can't communicate with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.04,1:17:00.27,en,,0,0,0,,I got an answer, but I have no idea what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.40,1:17:01.62,en,,0,0,0,,You ask him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.76,1:17:03.31,en,,0,0,0,,Take him down to the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.36,1:17:08.19,en,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You're coming with me for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.28,1:17:09.59,en,,0,0,0,,Come along. It won't cost anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.72,1:17:11.03,en,,0,0,0,,No need for cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.28,1:17:17.82,en,,0,0,0,,Why do you collect such things?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.92,1:17:19.91,en,,0,0,0,,He's deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.00,1:17:24.07,en,,0,0,0,,Are all these toys in here yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.60,1:18:02.59,en,,0,0,0,,-Freeze! -He can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.48,1:18:13.99,en,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.04,1:18:32.35,en,,0,0,0,,Sir! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.44,1:18:35.79,en,,0,0,0,,There's a deaf-mute running around. Find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.92,1:18:36.79,en,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.80,1:18:39.51,en,,0,0,0,,I didn't know he could fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.60,1:18:41.75,en,,0,0,0,,Neither did I. Go and find my gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.84,1:18:42.82,en,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.52,1:18:48.75,en,,0,0,0,,If we can manage to finance the buyout of Indian Ocean Bank,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.84,1:18:53.35,en,,0,0,0,,it would be a welcome addition to our portfolio.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.44,1:18:55.35,en,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fung, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.44,1:18:57.27,en,,0,0,0,,I said no calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.36,1:18:59.87,en,,0,0,0,,I know, but it's that man again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.20,1:19:02.39,en,,0,0,0,,Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.44,1:19:04.42,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.72,1:19:19.95,en,,0,0,0,,You called the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.16,1:19:22.23,en,,0,0,0,,No, you must be mistaken. We haven't!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.36,1:19:25.59,en,,0,0,0,,You needn't try and deceive us. We knew you'd go to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.72,1:19:27.27,en,,0,0,0,,To make you abandon that idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.36,1:19:30.03,en,,0,0,0,,we will demonstrate our power to you tomorrow at 12:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.20,1:19:33.98,en,,0,0,0,,We won't waste time bargaining with you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.16,1:19:38.03,en,,0,0,0,,After 12:00 tomorrow, if you decide it's prudent to pay the$20 million,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.16,1:19:41.07,en,,0,0,0,,place an ad in the name of your Zhiye Group
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.16,1:19:44.31,en,,0,0,0,,in one of the major newspapers the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.28,1:19:46.59,en,,0,0,0,,Call Mr. Lam!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.76,1:19:50.71,en,,0,0,0,,After 12:00 tomorrow, if you decide it's prudent to pay the$20 million,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.80,1:19:54.19,en,,0,0,0,,place an ad in the name of your Zhiye Group
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.28,1:19:56.79,en,,0,0,0,,in one of the major newspapers the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.88,1:19:57.94,en,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.04,1:19:59.43,en,,0,0,0,,Where was the call from?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.56,1:20:02.23,en,,0,0,0,,It was a modified mobile phone, so we couldn't trace it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.40,1:20:04.43,en,,0,0,0,,We knew you'd go to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.56,1:20:06.55,en,,0,0,0,,To make you abandon that idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.64,1:20:09.79,en,,0,0,0,,we will demonstrate our power to you tomorrow at 12:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.88,1:20:13.79,en,,0,0,0,,We won't waste time bargaining with you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.92,1:20:15.63,en,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, they're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.72,1:20:19.47,en,,0,0,0,,We've sent extra officers to protect your buildings.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.56,1:20:20.87,en,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.56,1:20:23.54,en,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.64,1:20:26.35,en,,0,0,0,,We will never tolerate such an outrage! It's time to act!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.48,1:20:27.35,en,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.00,1:20:31.98,en,,0,0,0,,Fay!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.88,1:20:33.83,en,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.32,1:20:36.43,en,,0,0,0,,Polar Bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.04,1:20:39.11,en,,0,0,0,,This is Ken. H&d like a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.32,1:20:42.83,en,,0,0,0,,I didn't snitch on you!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.96,1:20:45.99,en,,0,0,0,,Really? Then why did they turn up after you got caught?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.08,1:20:48.07,en,,0,0,0,,And why did they let you go so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.20,1:20:50.76,en,,0,0,0,,Lack of evidence. They granted me bail.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.72,1:20:53.83,en,,0,0,0,,I didn't snitch, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.92,1:20:58.35,en,,0,0,0,,It's all the same to us. We don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.44,1:21:01.23,en,,0,0,0,,-Where are we going? -Make any difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.36,1:21:02.58,en,,0,0,0,,-Miss Wong. -Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.68,1:21:05.43,en,,0,0,0,,-We've checked the mail. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.52,1:21:07.43,en,,0,0,0,,And these are for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.52,1:21:08.79,en,,0,0,0,,Who on earth sent those?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.88,1:21:10.59,en,,0,0,0,,Don't know. Someone special, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.68,1:21:12.27,en,,0,0,0,,If you don't know, who would?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.36,1:21:13.50,en,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.00,1:21:21.75,en,,0,0,0,,Plant this bomb and we're even.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.88,1:21:26.11,en,,0,0,0,,Do the job or you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.20,1:21:28.63,en,,0,0,0,,-Where shall I put it? -191 tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.72,1:21:29.75,en,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.96,1:21:37.87,en,,0,0,0,,Roger. Thanks a lot. Keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.40,1:21:42.51,en,,0,0,0,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.60,1:21:49.27,en,,0,0,0,,I'm a cop. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.40,1:21:50.87,en,,0,0,0,,I'm a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.68,1:22:06.95,en,,0,0,0,,ID card.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.72,1:22:11.19,en,,0,0,0,,-What? -Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.20,1:22:13.47,en,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.88,1:22:25.26,en,,0,0,0,,CID. Your case.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.36,1:22:27.03,en,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.04,1:22:35.15,en,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.24,1:22:36.75,en,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.84,1:22:38.47,en,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.40,1:22:44.47,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. CID. May I see your bag?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.32,1:22:54.54,en,,0,0,0,,The red bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.64,1:22:56.11,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. CID.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.68,1:23:11.03,en,,0,0,0,,Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.88,1:23:18.03,en,,0,0,0,,-It should be fine. -Here's the mail, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.88,1:23:21.23,en,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.80,1:23:24.15,en,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's a bluff?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.24,1:23:27.67,en,,0,0,0,,I hope so, but we can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.64,1:23:30.11,en,,0,0,0,,Okay. Keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.40,1:23:33.38,en,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.08,1:23:37.55,en,,0,0,0,,Ask her to wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.72,1:23:38.91,en,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.16,1:23:43.55,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, May's downstairs. She wants to talk to you urgently.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.48,1:23:46.46,en,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.04,1:23:52.35,en,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.08,1:23:56.91,en,,0,0,0,,I've written a letter for you. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.60,1:24:01.51,en,,0,0,0,,May. You came all this way to give me this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.64,1:24:04.71,en,,0,0,0,,It's important, so keep it safe. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.64,1:24:08.59,en,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, where's the scooter?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.68,1:24:11.79,en,,0,0,0,,We didn't get along, so I sold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.68,1:24:18.95,en,,0,0,0,,191 follow her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.56,1:24:32.31,en,,0,0,0,,I have my backup units in position.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.88,1:24:36.39,en,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think they're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.52,1:24:37.79,en,,0,0,0,,Then we should depend on the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.88,1:24:38.86,en,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.64,1:24:41.67,en,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.48,1:24:46.43,en,,0,0,0,,Get an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.56,1:24:47.70,en,,0,0,0,,Get the fire extinguisher.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.84,1:24:49.51,en,,0,0,0,,Call Mr. Lam.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.24,1:25:06.67,en,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.08,1:25:16.11,en,,0,0,0,,-Go and investigate. -Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.20,1:25:18.11,en,,0,0,0,,Don't panic. Ka Kui, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.20,1:25:19.91,en,,0,0,0,,Call the fire department. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.60,1:25:25.75,en,,0,0,0,,Bring a fire extinguisher.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.36,1:25:31.39,en,,0,0,0,,Come on. Put the fire out first.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.52,1:25:32.71,en,,0,0,0,,Come on, get moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.80,1:25:35.10,en,,0,0,0,,-Is the ambulance here? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.24,1:25:36.35,en,,0,0,0,,Go call them!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.44,1:25:41.91,en,,0,0,0,,We need more help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.00,1:25:44.43,en,,0,0,0,,-Phone, sir. -Bill, you take the phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.52,1:25:46.51,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, meet me upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.52,1:25:56.35,en,,0,0,0,,I thought you were supposed to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.60,1:26:02.55,en,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.68,1:26:04.83,en,,0,0,0,,Package bomb. Miss Wong lost an arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.72,1:26:14.03,en,,0,0,0,,THE ZHIYE GROUP, TOGETHER WITH EVERY HONG KONG CITIZEN,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.12,1:26:18.47,en,,0,0,0,,STRIVES TO PRESERVE THE BEAUTY OF HONG KONG
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.04,1:26:23.35,en,,0,0,0,,-How's Miss Wong? -She's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.44,1:26:25.43,en,,0,0,0,,The doctor said her arm would recover.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.48,1:26:28.99,en,,0,0,0,,They'll do a skin graft on her face later.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.12,1:26:31.59,en,,0,0,0,,So we'll wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.68,1:26:35.55,en,,0,0,0,,Wong's decided to pay up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.04,1:26:37.95,en,,0,0,0,,What am I going to tell Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.88,1:26:41.95,en,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bill, that's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.04,1:26:43.75,en,,0,0,0,,We always said it was going to be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.88,1:26:47.15,en,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with well-organised criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.24,1:26:51.43,en,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd blown me up instead. I don't like putting lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.56,1:26:53.19,en,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.28,1:26:55.55,en,,0,0,0,,If they come to collect the money, I'm sure we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.64,1:26:59.67,en,,0,0,0,,If I pass on what you said to Raymond, he won't be happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.76,1:27:01.39,en,,0,0,0,,What we need is real action.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.40,1:27:04.59,en,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.60,1:27:08.15,en,,0,0,0,,I guess you've seen the papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.24,1:27:10.19,en,,0,0,0,,Now what do I tell the Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.64,1:27:19.55,en,,0,0,0,,That's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.64,1:27:21.59,en,,0,0,0,,We always said it'd be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.72,1:27:25.47,en,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with well-organised criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.28,1:27:28.84,en,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd blown me up instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.92,1:27:31.30,en,,0,0,0,,I don't like putting lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.40,1:27:32.79,en,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.88,1:27:37.31,en,,0,0,0,,If they come to collect the money, I'm sure we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.40,1:27:40.15,en,,0,0,0,,All this is talk. What we need is some real action.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.88,1:27:54.39,en,,0,0,0,,Something's up. Raymond's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.04,1:27:59.59,en,,0,0,0,,That's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.68,1:28:02.03,en,,0,0,0,,We always said it'd be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.12,1:28:05.31,en,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with well-organised criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.36,1:28:10.90,en,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd blown me up instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.00,1:28:12.71,en,,0,0,0,,I don't like putting lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.80,1:28:13.99,en,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.08,1:28:16.38,en,,0,0,0,,If they come to collect, I'm sure we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.56,1:28:20.23,en,,0,0,0,,I understand your situation, and I'll note it in the report.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.32,1:28:23.67,en,,0,0,0,,Good luck with the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.20,1:28:33.42,en,,0,0,0,,You come, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.80,1:28:38.35,en,,0,0,0,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.44,1:28:40.35,en,,0,0,0,,Did you two have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.44,1:28:42.55,en,,0,0,0,,Right. But this is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.16,1:28:56.11,en,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.76,1:28:57.90,en,,0,0,0,,I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.00,1:28:59.14,en,,0,0,0,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.64,1:29:02.23,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.36,1:29:03.31,en,,0,0,0,,Put it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.20,1:29:06.03,en,,0,0,0,,Right. Put it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.00,1:29:09.35,en,,0,0,0,,-Hello? -Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.48,1:29:10.91,en,,0,0,0,,May's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.04,1:29:11.99,en,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.12,1:29:15.43,en,,0,0,0,,We'd just left the shop when someone dragged her into a van.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.56,1:29:16.99,en,,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.16,1:29:20.47,en,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But it must have something to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.56,1:29:22.39,en,,0,0,0,,Could it be those thugs again?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.52,1:29:23.91,en,,0,0,0,,Chu Tu.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.40,1:29:27.67,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui! Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.08,1:29:34.11,en,,0,0,0,,-Ka Kui! What's up? -An old score. May's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.20,1:29:35.18,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.72,1:29:38.19,en,,0,0,0,,-What happened? -May's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.32,1:29:41.79,en,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Sign this cheque before you're dead. Our brothers...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.88,1:29:43.87,en,,0,0,0,,-Please stop. He's a patient. -Let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.96,1:29:46.47,en,,0,0,0,,We did what you asked. That's why we deserve something.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.56,1:29:48.43,en,,0,0,0,,You won't need any money when you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.88,1:30:03.86,en,,0,0,0,,Chu Tu!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.96,1:30:09.42,en,,0,0,0,,-Chu Tu! -Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.12,1:30:46.39,en,,0,0,0,,Chu Tu!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.60,1:30:51.87,en,,0,0,0,,Bring May back!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.96,1:30:54.23,en,,0,0,0,,I know nothing! I did nothing! It's him! Him!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.00,1:30:58.31,en,,0,0,0,,Bring May back!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.36,1:31:01.23,en,,0,0,0,,Sir, you can't do that to a patient! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.32,1:31:02.75,en,,0,0,0,,Put him down!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.88,1:31:04.35,en,,0,0,0,,Speak up! What have you done with May?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.52,1:31:06.95,en,,0,0,0,,-I didn't take her. -Who did, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.08,1:31:10.51,en,,0,0,0,,I was very nasty to you before... but now I'm sick and penniless.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.56,1:31:12.83,en,,0,0,0,,What reason would I have for taking her?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.96,1:31:15.23,en,,0,0,0,,If he did have any money, he'd be pouring it into treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.32,1:31:18.03,en,,0,0,0,,This is none of our doing. Hassling you was business, not personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.20,1:31:20.23,en,,0,0,0,,We only did it on account of the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.72,1:31:23.07,en,,0,0,0,,Then who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.04,1:31:27.99,en,,0,0,0,,There's a phone over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.08,1:31:29.79,en,,0,0,0,,Don't die before you sign this!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.92,1:31:32.03,en,,0,0,0,,You! I've had about enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.16,1:31:36.03,en,,0,0,0,,He's got one foot in the grave, so what do I care?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.88,1:31:50.99,en,,0,0,0,,-Hello, this is 1378. -Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.08,1:31:52.67,en,,0,0,0,,May!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.76,1:31:54.23,en,,0,0,0,,You recognise her voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.36,1:31:56.51,en,,0,0,0,,We're at the Hung Fung Industrial Building.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.60,1:31:58.59,en,,0,0,0,,Who is this? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.68,1:32:01.51,en,,0,0,0,,Come alone or she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.60,1:32:02.58,en,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.64,1:32:04.62,en,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.04,1:32:07.43,en,,0,0,0,,I know where that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.24,1:32:44.22,en,,0,0,0,,May!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.88,1:32:47.07,en,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.40,1:32:51.59,en,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.68,1:32:52.79,en,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.96,1:32:55.03,en,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. Why have you kidnapped her?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.16,1:32:58.15,en,,0,0,0,,"Ka Kui, by the time you read this letter..."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.24,1:32:59.22,en,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.32,1:33:01.39,en,,0,0,0,,"...I've decided we should be apart."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.48,1:33:02.70,en,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.80,1:33:05.47,en,,0,0,0,,"I don't think I'll see you again."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.60,1:33:07.71,en,,0,0,0,,It's a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.96,1:33:12.79,en,,0,0,0,,Just like they say... unlucky in love, lucky in money.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.88,1:33:13.75,en,,0,0,0,,There's more.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.88,1:33:15.07,en,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.20,1:33:19.35,en,,0,0,0,,"When we first met, I thought you liked your job very much,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.44,1:33:22.23,en,,0,0,0,,"and you'd be my Mr. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.36,1:33:27.48,en,,0,0,0,,"Now I realise the only thing that matters in your life is your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.56,1:33:31.99,en,,0,0,0,,"I tell myself what made me fall in love with you
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.12,1:33:35.35,en,,0,0,0,,"is also what makes me want to leave you."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.56,1:33:39.23,en,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why? Why did you break up?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.24,1:33:45.47,en,,0,0,0,,"You told me you didn't want me involved with your work,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.56,1:33:46.99,en,,0,0,0,,"but I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.08,1:33:49.83,en,,0,0,0,,"What I did mind, though, is that you never spent enough time with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.92,1:33:52.59,en,,0,0,0,,"Being with you was the happiest time of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.68,1:33:58.15,en,,0,0,0,,"But when you weren't there, it was the worst time of my life."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.24,1:33:59.55,en,,0,0,0,,That's just not right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.64,1:34:00.83,en,,0,0,0,,"If I didn't leave you,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.96,1:34:06.47,en,,0,0,0,,"I'd spend my life waiting for you to come home!"
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.56,1:34:08.31,en,,0,0,0,,Can't you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.88,1:34:13.35,en,,0,0,0,,She's crying!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.44,1:34:14.63,en,,0,0,0,,So is he.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.36,1:34:17.99,en,,0,0,0,,Keep reading, go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.12,1:34:22.23,en,,0,0,0,,"...because you can never stop being a policeman."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.32,1:34:24.59,en,,0,0,0,,A policeman who never stops.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.72,1:34:25.83,en,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.08,1:34:29.83,en,,0,0,0,,"I think it's the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.76,1:34:35.07,en,,0,0,0,,"Please forgive me for making such a selfish choice. May."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.88,1:34:40.83,en,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.96,1:34:43.87,en,,0,0,0,,We want you to help us get rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.84,1:34:47.75,en,,0,0,0,,You must have heard the Zhiye Group was blackmailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.76,1:34:52.55,en,,0,0,0,,The hardest part of the job is the pick-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.40,1:34:55.99,en,,0,0,0,,You'll collect the ransom for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.12,1:34:57.26,en,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.40,1:34:58.91,en,,0,0,0,,You don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.00,1:35:01.43,en,,0,0,0,,He said no.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.88,1:35:11.43,en,,0,0,0,,I think you'll enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.04,1:35:15.47,en,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.20,1:35:17.18,en,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.16,1:35:20.67,en,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.80,1:35:22.55,en,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.28,1:35:26.47,en,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.80,1:35:30.27,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.88,1:35:33.10,en,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.72,1:35:37.71,en,,0,0,0,,So you want to play the hero?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.60,1:35:57.15,en,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.48,1:36:10.95,en,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.92,1:36:24.98,en,,0,0,0,,You rotten swine!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.64,1:36:28.95,en,,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.04,1:36:30.02,en,,0,0,0,,Kill me if you've got the guts.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.16,1:36:31.95,en,,0,0,0,,So tough!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.04,1:36:35.91,en,,0,0,0,,Really? Let's see if his girl is tough, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.36,1:36:39.75,en,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.68,1:36:44.06,en,,0,0,0,,How's that? How's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.28,1:36:51.71,en,,0,0,0,,Enough! You've made your point.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.08,1:36:54.39,en,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.00,1:36:57.63,en,,0,0,0,,Just let her go. I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.76,1:37:01.15,en,,0,0,0,,We won't let her go unless you help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.24,1:37:02.63,en,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.76,1:37:05.11,en,,0,0,0,,Collect the money for us. Then 191 let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.44,1:37:07.39,en,,0,0,0,,You don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.24,1:37:18.27,en,,0,0,0,,191 do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.40,1:37:19.38,en,,0,0,0,,Good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.68,1:37:46.51,en,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't advise you to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.64,1:37:48.87,en,,0,0,0,,Break one wire and the whole thing blows.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.20,1:37:52.71,en,,0,0,0,,The same thing happens if I press this button.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.16,1:38:01.35,en,,0,0,0,,You'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.52,1:38:19.47,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.72,1:38:23.86,en,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.24,1:38:26.46,en,,0,0,0,,I'll come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.80,1:38:44.02,en,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.16,1:38:45.95,en,,0,0,0,,-He's on the line. -Trace the call!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.04,1:38:46.99,en,,0,0,0,,I'll get Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.40,1:38:52.63,en,,0,0,0,,Is the money ready? We91 collect it in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.76,1:38:53.82,en,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.96,1:38:55.87,en,,0,0,0,,-Did you call the cops? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.04,1:39:09.95,en,,0,0,0,,Where's Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.08,1:39:11.11,en,,0,0,0,,I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.76,1:39:13.79,en,,0,0,0,,How could he be so irresponsible?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.88,1:39:17.07,en,,0,0,0,,I can't wait. Don't take any risks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.16,1:39:18.07,en,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.24,1:39:29.63,en,,0,0,0,,You'll have ten minutes to get back here again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.72,1:39:31.07,en,,0,0,0,,No tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.16,1:39:34.83,en,,0,0,0,,If we don't get our money, your vest will go bang!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.52,1:39:37.99,en,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.24,1:39:40.38,en,,0,0,0,,Get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.40,1:39:46.54,en,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.40,1:39:55.31,en,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.44,1:39:56.95,en,,0,0,0,,Police.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.68,1:40:00.99,en,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Fung. -Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.08,1:40:02.51,en,,0,0,0,,You will pay me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.60,1:40:05.59,en,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.72,1:40:10.99,en,,0,0,0,,You promised to let us bug the phones.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.08,1:40:13.03,en,,0,0,0,,We could trace the calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.16,1:40:14.95,en,,0,0,0,,It's too bad you can't handle the bomb case so effectively.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.08,1:40:16.47,en,,0,0,0,,We have everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.56,1:40:17.99,en,,0,0,0,,Once they pay the money, we move into action.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.12,1:40:20.35,en,,0,0,0,,I hope you won't do anything to make matters worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.48,1:40:22.35,en,,0,0,0,,Because this will encourage the bombers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.48,1:40:25.67,en,,0,0,0,,So the police couldn't help. We could only depend on ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.48,1:40:34.03,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, the boss was looking...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.12,1:40:35.07,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.68,1:40:36.66,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.84,1:40:39.83,en,,0,0,0,,-Ka Kui! -Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.12,1:40:43.23,en,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.36,1:40:45.39,en,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.00,1:40:48.51,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.80,1:40:53.02,en,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.24,1:40:57.55,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.68,1:40:59.39,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.52,1:41:01.98,en,,0,0,0,,Never mind. I'm here to collect the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.12,1:41:03.55,en,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.64,1:41:05.91,en,,0,0,0,,-Is he your man? -Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.08,1:41:07.14,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.28,1:41:10.67,en,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time. The money!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.36,1:41:19.99,en,,0,0,0,,-What are you doing? -Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.12,1:41:22.50,en,,0,0,0,,Move and 191 shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.68,1:41:23.95,en,,0,0,0,,Don't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.08,1:41:26.39,en,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.48,1:41:27.46,en,,0,0,0,,Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.64,1:41:31.83,en,,0,0,0,,If you shoot me, everybody here...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.68,1:41:34.43,en,,0,0,0,,...will be blown sky high.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.88,1:41:40.11,en,,0,0,0,,If one wire breaks, the whole thing will explode!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.12,1:41:43.31,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.40,1:41:45.07,en,,0,0,0,,Can't we work this out?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.24,1:41:47.83,en,,0,0,0,,If I don't leave here in ten minutes, it will go off.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.92,1:41:49.71,en,,0,0,0,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.28,1:42:03.55,en,,0,0,0,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.12,1:42:11.19,en,,0,0,0,,Attention all units! Do not stop Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.84,1:42:24.51,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui! Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.64,1:42:25.70,en,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.20,1:42:31.91,en,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.12,1:42:44.83,en,,0,0,0,,-I think he did it. -Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.56,1:42:49.94,en,,0,0,0,,-Looks like he was followed. -Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.52,1:43:15.83,en,,0,0,0,,Tell him to move up.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.32,1:43:24.27,en,,0,0,0,,Give me the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.40,1:43:28.15,en,,0,0,0,,I'm being followed. Let me shake them off first.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.24,1:43:29.79,en,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.84,1:43:39.39,en,,0,0,0,,Are the cops behind us?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.64,1:43:51.15,en,,0,0,0,,Stay back! Don't come near!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.12,1:44:02.91,en,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.76,1:44:10.71,en,,0,0,0,,-What are you doing? -What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.80,1:44:12.99,en,,0,0,0,,A bomb's about to blow. Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.12,1:44:14.31,en,,0,0,0,,A bomb! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.40,1:44:36.62,en,,0,0,0,,There's no cops!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.72,1:44:38.43,en,,0,0,0,,191 blow him to bits.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.52,1:44:40.95,en,,0,0,0,,Wait! What about the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.04,1:44:43.71,en,,0,0,0,,And you can't get a radio signal in the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.80,1:44:44.75,en,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.88,1:44:47.87,en,,0,0,0,,-We've got the girl. Don't worry. -Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.68,1:46:26.23,en,,0,0,0,,If anything goes wrong, kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.00,1:47:27.35,en,,0,0,0,,Where is May?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.52,1:47:35.11,en,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.00,1:47:58.51,en,,0,0,0,,Look, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.40,1:48:05.59,en,,0,0,0,,I told you he wouldn't play tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.80,1:48:28.83,en,,0,0,0,,May!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.80,1:48:36.27,en,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.68,1:48:48.11,en,,0,0,0,,Freeze! You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.24,1:48:49.87,en,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.00,1:48:53.23,en,,0,0,0,,Come on then, arrest us.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.36,1:48:55.23,en,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.32,1:48:57.15,en,,0,0,0,,Move and 191 shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.36,1:49:01.35,en,,0,0,0,,You think so? You'd have to shoot fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.44,1:49:03.03,en,,0,0,0,,There are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.16,1:49:04.38,en,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.48,1:49:07.11,en,,0,0,0,,If I don't shoot you, you'll only spend a few years in jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.20,1:49:09.79,en,,0,0,0,,And then you'll be a reformed person. That's better than dying in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.92,1:49:14.03,en,,0,0,0,,Better to die than to live as a pauper. We are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.64,1:49:15.70,en,,0,0,0,,We want to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.84,1:49:19.59,en,,0,0,0,,There's no shame in wanting wealth. But your way is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.72,1:49:21.87,en,,0,0,0,,So what is right and what is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.00,1:49:24.56,en,,0,0,0,,You can get everything you want in life
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.64,1:49:27.63,en,,0,0,0,,by helping other people get what they want in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.04,1:49:33.11,en,,0,0,0,,You'd have a whole new outlook. That's what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.20,1:49:36.19,en,,0,0,0,,But what you have done now has hurt society.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.28,1:49:38.66,en,,0,0,0,,-This benefits no-one. -What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.84,1:49:41.55,en,,0,0,0,,Other than you guys, who thinks you're doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.64,1:49:43.03,en,,0,0,0,,Who would think highly of your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.32,1:49:47.59,en,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.68,1:49:49.39,en,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.52,1:49:52.08,en,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound too bad... but there's still one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.16,1:49:56.59,en,,0,0,0,,We might take your advice if we had certain opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.68,1:49:58.23,en,,0,0,0,,See, we don't want to go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.36,1:50:00.07,en,,0,0,0,,We don't want to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.00,1:50:03.67,en,,0,0,0,,Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.76,1:50:05.75,en,,0,0,0,,Run! This is a fireworks factory.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.52,1:52:30.71,en,,0,0,0,,-May! -I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.84,1:52:32.39,en,,0,0,0,,May, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.08,1:52:41.07,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.68,1:53:05.07,en,,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.40,1:53:17.19,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui! Come here! There's the rubbish chute.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.16,1:53:31.67,en,,0,0,0,,There's an exit.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.16,1:53:35.51,en,,0,0,0,,May, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.20,1:53:42.87,en,,0,0,0,,It looks too high.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.04,1:53:44.87,en,,0,0,0,,Just jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.04,1:54:07.87,en,,0,0,0,,Ka Kui, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.96,1:54:11.59,en,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Get out of here, May. Go as far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.68,1:54:13.19,en,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.16,1:56:34.19,en,,0,0,0,,How do you like it? Want some more? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.32,1:56:37.03,en,,0,0,0,,How about some more, you little bastard?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.12,1:56:39.79,en,,0,0,0,,Want some more?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.32,1:56:43.51,en,,0,0,0,,Want some more? Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.68,1:56:47.15,en,,0,0,0,,Want some more?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.16,1:56:51.14,en,,0,0,0,,More?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.84,1:57:36.67,en,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.08,1:58:35.47,en,,0,0,0,,Stop crying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.48,1:58:38.31,en,,0,0,0,,Look. The fireworks are beautiful.
